Put the following text into your AndroidManifest.xml inside the <Application></Application> tags

        <activity 
            android:name=".SplashscreenActivity"
            android:label="@string/app_name"
            android:screenOrientation="portrait">
            <intent-filter>
                <action android:name="android.intent.action.MAIN"/>
                <category android:name="android.intent.category.LAUNCHER"/>
            </intent-filter>
        </activity>
        <activity
            android:name="com.mycompany.app.appname.ActivityAfterSplash"
            android:label="@string/app_name"
            android:screenOrientation="portrait" >
            <intent-filter>
                <action android:name="com.mycompany.app.appname.ACTIVITYAFTERSPLASH" />
                <category android:name="android.intent.category.DEFAULT" />
            </intent-filter>
        </activity>
        
Enjoy!